<CELL>8&mdash;10</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>The Duties of Women,</CELL>
<CELL>11&mdash;13</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>3. He &s;hews what Timothy &s;hould teach,</CELL>
<CELL>14&mdash;C. iv. 1&mdash;6</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>What he &s;hould avoid,</CELL>
<CELL>7&mdash;11</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>What follow after,</CELL>
<CELL>12&mdash;16</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>How he &s;hould treat Men and Women,</CELL>
<CELL>C. v. 1&mdash;2</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>Widows,</CELL>
<CELL>3&mdash;16</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>Elders,</CELL>
<CELL>17&mdash;19</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>Offenders,</CELL>
<CELL>20&mdash;21</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>Him&s;elf,</CELL>
<CELL>22&mdash;23</CELL>
